data.description: 3 Family home! Live in one unit and have the other 2 units help pay your mortgage or add to your portfolio! Delivered VACANT! Walk-in level has a 1bdrm/1bth apt (vacant). On this level can also access sep utilities room that has boiler, a separate room that can be used as storage, and access to the back yard. 1st floor unit is a 3bdrms/1bth apt (rented but tenant will be moving out) with eat in kitchen & separate living rm area. 2nd floor unit is a 4bdrms/1bth apt (vacant), the floors have been redone and freshly painted, with eat in kitchen & separate living room as well. Conveniently located steps away from multiple bus lines Bx 40,42 on E 180st, and bx 41 on webster ave. Trains B/D (182-183st station) & 4 train (183st station), metro north just about a block away, take it to NYC and be there in minutes. District 10 schools (PS 23 & PS 59). Hospitals (St Barnabas), shopping hubs and restaurants both on E Tremont ave & Fordham Rd. Close to major highways (I95, & Bronx River pkwy).
